The '''Yomm family''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] family from [[Roon/Legends|Roon]] who lived in the [[Umboo]] province. They were friends of [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] and [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]]. Members included the famous doctor [[Nilz Yomm]], his wife [[Bola Yomm]], and a champion of the [[Roon Colonial Games]], [[Auren Yomm Baobab|Auren Yomm]].

